      "title" : "The day you let grime run the clock from midnight to sunset",
      "description" : "Overnight, “Nuestra Canción” and “La vie en rose” set a gentle tone before the morning launched into a relentless UK grime and drill circuit—BexBlu, Damzz, and Nemzzz looping through every hour. By evening, jazz rap and Latin indie flickered in, but the grime pulse never let up. 522 minutes, 232 tracks, 74 artists—your biggest music day of the year.",
